header.gameNote: SUN BELT CONFERENCE MEN'S CHAMPIONSHIP - FINAL

videos.description: DeVon Walker gets open to make the layup and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Troy's Walker drives down to make the layup and-1

videos.description: Alex Hicks with a huge block. Hicks getting second block of the game.
videos.headline: Alex Hicks sends the ball to the stands

videos.description: Daniel Peace finds an open Alex Hicks. Hicks comes in with a slam dunk.
videos.headline: Hicks slams it down to give Troy the lead

videos.description: Kavin Gilder-Tilbury puts up a long 3-pointer. Gets it in and draws the foul.
videos.headline: Bobcats' Kavin Gilder-Tilbury with a huge 3

videos.description: Nijal Pearson blocks the shot and runs the court to make a clutch layup.
videos.headline: Nijal Pearson with a block and an and-1

videos.description: Troy beats Texas State 59-53 to win the Sun Belt championship and punches their ticket to the big tournament.
videos.headline: Trojans wins Sun Belt title and gets NCAA bid
